{
  "stem": "1753.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then I see the last, must have been, the last transport on that day that came to that-- to Treblinka II for the group of Jews from the Bialystok ghetto arrived that day to be exterminated.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And I remembered just like this very second.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I can see it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because we were-- our [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] car, railroad car, was parallel with a cattle car, right-- a few feet over.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I remember one lady shouting down to the Ukrainians, [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] [POLISH SPEECH] What this means, for the people that don't understand Polish, today it's us, and tomorrow it's you.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And you talk about the emotions.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "When I think about that particular episode, I get goose pimples because I remember it like it would have been just two minutes before.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But what we subsequently learned, that group that came from Bialystok, you only can estimate maybe 500, 800 people.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the gas chambers, one no longer functioning, they were shot and burned into the-- in the pit that was also there near Treblinka II.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So ultimately, they couldn't do much with us, and, in fact, they needed us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Because when we got back to camp II, we found out there was an uprising there too.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they eliminated just about everybody there, including the kapos that were involved in the uprising and some of the other people that worked in the-- in-- in the offices.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "A couple of German guys that spoke German, and they worked in the offices for the Germans.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And the people from the laundry, from the Jewish laundry, and the people that-- and-- and the water carriers, and so on, They were all involved.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "In fact they got to the gun [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] storage place.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
